   1. Frontend (UI Layer)                        1. Frontend (UI Layer)
   - HTML â†’ Structure                             - XML â†’ Structure (layouts, widgets)
   - CSS  â†’ Styling                               - Resources (colors.xml, styles.xml, drawables)
   - JS   â†’ Logic/Interactivity                   - Java/Kotlin â†’ Logic (events, actions)

   2. Communication Layer                         2. Communication Layer
   - fetch/axios â†’ API call                       - Retrofit/Volley/OkHttp â†’ API call
   - JSON response from server                    - JSON response from server

   3. Backend (Server + Logic)                    3. Backend (Server + Logic)
